"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"A wave of violence has erupted across Mexico after a powerful drug cartel boss died following his capture by special forces.\",            \"english_title\": \"Violence in Mexico\",            \"translated_version\": \"Una ola de violencia ha comenzado en M\u00e9xico despu\u00e9s de que un jefe de cartel de drogas muri\u00f3 tras ser capturado por fuerzas especiales.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Violencia en M\u00e9xico\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A major snowstorm hit the US north-east, causing disruptions for millions of people and leading to thousands of flight cancellations.\",            \"english_title\": \"Snowstorm in US\",            \"translated_version\": \"Una gran tormenta de nieve golpe\u00f3 el noreste de EE.UU., causando problemas para millones de personas y llevando a miles de vuelos cancelados.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tormenta de nieve en EE.UU.\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The State Department has ordered non-essential staff to leave the embassy in Beirut after reviewing security.\",            \"english_title\": \"Embassy Staff Ordered to Leave\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Departamento de Estado ha ordenado al personal no esencial que salga de la embajada en Beirut despu\u00e9s de revisar la seguridad.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Personal de embajada debe salir\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Steve Rosenberg reports on the economic consequences of Russia's war and how people are coping with the situation.\",            \"english_title\": \"Economic Impact of Russia's War\",            \"translated_version\": \"Steve Rosenberg informa sobre las consecuencias econ\u00f3micas de la guerra de Rusia y c\u00f3mo la gente est\u00e1 manejando la situaci\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Impacto econ\u00f3mico de la guerra de Rusia\"        },        {   